subject: Paramaters Collection type
msgSnippet: Hi, Is there any particular reason why the JavaDoc and numerous examples state that the return of a @Parameters method is Collection, when it in fact it may
messageBody:
Hi,

Is there any particular reason why the JavaDoc and numerous examples state
that the return of a @Parameters method is Collection, when it in fact it
may only be a List<Object[]>?
